# RealSmart app shell

All authenticated RealSmart apps share one layout shell. **Extend it; do not replace it.**

## Layout zones (left to right)

1. **Suite switcher** — `x-nav.suite-switcher`
2. **Icon rail** — `w-14` dark rail; `x-nav.rail-link` for top-level areas
3. **Collapsible sidebar** — `x-nav.sidebar-link`
4. **Main content** — header + scrollable page body

Canonical shell sync: `~/Developer/realsmart-shell/bin/sync.sh`

## Do not

- Build a different nav pattern (Flux sidebar as primary chrome)
- Hard-code suite URLs — use `config/realsmart.php` and env vars
